platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Once you start playing Lifeline 2, its almost impossible to stop thinking about what its main character, Arika, is up to. Thats because this riveting text adventure consists of one long back-and-forth conversation between the two of you, with the games events occurring in real time. Arikas messages come to you through notifications on your device, and you pick one of two responses; each of your choices affects how the fantasy-based story pans out. Helping her on her mission to save her brother and avenge her parents kept us spellbound the whole way through.
